He's got some juice here.

883
00:59:30,442 --> 00:59:32,490
Mr. Baker, could you tell me anything...

884
00:59:32,652 --> 00:59:33,778
...about Henri Young?

885
00:59:33,945 --> 00:59:36,243
Don't know Henri Young.

886
00:59:36,907 --> 00:59:40,457
Could you tell us anything
about Mr. Glenn?

887
00:59:41,703 --> 00:59:44,832
Warden Glenn has always been
good to me.

888
00:59:46,708 --> 00:59:49,211
Have you ever been in the dungeons?

889
00:59:49,503 --> 00:59:51,756
Ma'am, I don't know nothing
about no dungeons.

890
00:59:52,672 --> 00:59:56,302
That's all, ma'am. I gotta go now.

891
01:00:00,097 --> 01:00:01,690
Fuck you.

892
01:00:01,848 --> 01:00:03,065
Did Mr. Glenn tell you...

893
01:00:03,225 --> 01:00:04,852
...not to cooperate with me?

894
01:00:05,018 --> 01:00:06,565
Fuck you.

895
01:00:06,728 --> 01:00:09,231
Where are the dungeons located?

896
01:00:09,397 --> 01:00:12,401
Don't take my fucking picture.

