913
01:01:19,718 --> 01:01:21,971
The old Citadel, the sub-level of the prison.

914
01:01:22,137 --> 01:01:26,768
That's mostly storage,
a few solitary cells. No dungeons.

915
01:01:26,933 --> 01:01:30,233
I would like to see
the solitary-confinement cells.

916
01:01:30,395 --> 01:01:32,989
I would love to show those cells to you,
but I can't.

917
01:01:33,148 --> 01:01:37,528
They're an insurance risk to visitors in case
of a riot. We won't be able to protect you.

918
01:01:37,694 --> 01:01:39,617
Thank you for your concern.

919
01:01:39,779 --> 01:01:42,032
I could show you
the exercise yard, though.

920
01:01:42,949 --> 01:01:45,202
You have papers.

921
01:01:45,368 --> 01:01:48,417
Yes, I have papers.
So you can cut the good-guy act.

922
01:01:48,580 --> 01:01:52,756
Mr. Stamphill, the fact is I do consider
myself as one of the good guys...

923
01:01:52,918 --> 01:01:57,139
...and perhaps more than you,
I know what the bad guys are like.

924
01:01:57,297 --> 01:01:59,800
No, no, no. I'd like to read them. Please.

925
01:02:01,134 --> 01:02:02,636
Thank you.

926
01:02:04,304 --> 01:02:05,476
