941
01:02:53,311 --> 01:02:54,528
Thanks, Mike.

942
01:02:54,688 --> 01:02:55,905
I just need some air.

943
01:03:19,462 --> 01:03:21,430
My God.

944
01:03:41,401 --> 01:03:45,247
Listen, my name's James Stamphill.
I'm Henri Young's attorney.

945
01:03:45,405 --> 01:03:47,954
I can force them to let you out
so you can testify...

946
01:03:48,116 --> 01:03:49,959
...in San Francisco in a court of law.

947
01:03:50,118 --> 01:03:54,248
You just have to give me your name.
I promise I will do what I said for you.

948
01:04:08,636 --> 01:04:09,762
Hey, James, she's okay.

949
01:04:09,929 --> 01:04:11,772
Just needed some air.

950
01:04:15,143 --> 01:04:18,272
Can we go now?
- Feeling any better?

951
01:04:19,105 --> 01:04:21,278
I guess I'll make it.

952
01:04:24,569 --> 01:04:28,073
- Did you get anything?
- I got three names.

953
01:04:28,782 --> 01:04:30,409
Let's go.

954
01:04:31,409 --> 01:04:34,083
Where did Stamphill get
the three names on this list?

955
01:04:37,791 --> 01:04:39,008
I don't know, Mr. Henkin.

956
01:04:39,167 --> 01:04:41,215
You think you can trust these cons?

957
01:04:41,378 --> 01:04:43,801
They're smart enough
to look after their interests.

958
01:04:43,963 --> 01:04:47,183
They told Glenn your boy James said
he'd get them out of solitary...

959
01:04:47,342 --> 01:04:50,186
...as long as they testify for the defense
and lie on the stand.

960
01:04:50,345 --> 01:04:51,392
