in the Justice Department.

1076
01:12:15,081 --> 01:12:17,675
I'm just telling you what the score
is, Byron.

1077
01:12:17,834 --> 01:12:20,257
It's up to you to take care of him.

1078
01:12:22,171 --> 01:12:25,175
Why would J. Edgar Hoover care
about what happens to Henri Young?

1079
01:12:25,341 --> 01:12:26,558
Grow up, James.

1080
01:12:26,717 --> 01:12:28,515
He doesn't care
about what happens to Henri.

1081
01:12:28,678 --> 01:12:33,775
