1083
01:12:35,852 --> 01:12:38,480
He can't have some kid
from the PD's office-

1084
01:12:38,646 --> 01:12:40,944
I'm not a public defender anymore.

1085
01:12:41,107 --> 01:12:42,950
Don't play games. You know the point.

1086
01:12:43,109 --> 01:12:47,114
Yeah. The point is I'm trying to do
what's right. I'm talking about justice here.

1087
01:12:47,280 --> 01:12:51,410
You're disgusted about what happened
on Alcatraz. So am I.

1088
01:12:51,576 --> 01:12:56,958
But if you tear the whole system down,
what does that say about America?

1089
01:12:57,123 --> 01:12:58,966
We're wrong.

1090
01:12:59,542 --> 01:13:01,465
