1093
01:13:08,926 --> 01:13:13,272
Byron, we're talking about one man here.
It's not that big of a deal.

1094
01:13:13,598 --> 01:13:16,568
- You're under surveillance.
- What?

1095
01:13:16,767 --> 01:13:20,317
Everyone is watching you.
Tell me how you plan to continue.

1096
01:13:21,814 --> 01:13:26,320
You have to realize, no one will talk.
Everyone has been gotten to.

1097
01:13:27,612 --> 01:13:29,580
I have somebody.

1098
01:13:29,739 --> 01:13:31,241
Who?

1099
01:13:32,825 --> 01:13:34,953
I can't tell you.

1100
01:13:35,453 --> 01:13:39,174
- So now you don't trust me?
- Byron, you're my brother. I love you.

1101
01:13:39,790 --> 01:13:41,463
