1127
01:15:25,604 --> 01:15:27,732
Mr. Simpson, do you hold
any sort of grudge...

1128
01:15:27,898 --> 01:15:30,242
...against Warden Humson
or Associate Warden Glenn?

1129
01:15:30,401 --> 01:15:31,778
